==English==
===Noun===
'''arithmetic series''' (''plural'' '''arithmetic series''') <!--plural is the same as the singular-->

#{{analysis}} A [[series]] in which the result of subtracting any term from the next gives a [[constant]] value, known as the [[common difference]] of the series.

